      "para_id": "Q001835.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Namzid-tara , child of Ur-Nanibgal , governor of Nibru , is your servant ."
    }
